Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋 随着轰的一声 \NIn the beginning, there was darkness. And then… BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的时间 空间和物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所见超乎我们的想象 超越了客观认知极限 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined beyond the limits of our existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙" \Nin a place we call… THE UNIVERSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中只有我们吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are we alone in the Universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们在观看奇妙的行星吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are we the only ones who look up at the stars and wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"还有外族存在吗？"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Is anybody out there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天科学家用不同的方法来确定答案 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today, scientists quest for the answer in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的利用大型的无线电设备 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some with massive radio telescopes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的利用外层空间探测器 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some with interplanetarian, interstellar probes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们发现了外层空间的生命 那会是何种景象？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we find extraterrestrial life, what will it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔软糊状的组织？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Soft and squishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者我们最初接触的外星人 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or will the first aliens we contact
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是自我复制机体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}simple be self-replicating machines,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的生物形体已经消亡数百万年？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}their biological creators having died off millions of years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上最高级别的科学家在寻找答案 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some of the top scientists in the world probe for answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找外星人 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the search for E.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0001,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://www.hdcmct.com{\r}
